Class GetProduct

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.j2bugzilla.rpc.GetProduct
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BugzillaMethod

    public class GetProduct
extends Object
implements BugzillaMethod
    The GetProduct class provides access to information on Products active in a particular Bugzilla installation.
    Author:
    Tom

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      GetProduct(int id)
      Creates a new GetProduct, which can be used to retrieve the Product associated with the specified ID number.
      GetProduct(int[] ids)
      Creates a new GetProduct, which can be used to retrieve the collection of Product associated with the specified ID numbers.
